node.text:
Chai Cider is BACK and arriving on shelves soon! Bursting with cinnamon and nutmeg it's perfect for sliding from summer into fall. 🍎 🍁 

Keep an eye out for Chai Cider over the next few weeks. P.S. It's available now in our Mercantile Shop!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Brewery Ommegang on August 09, 2021. May be an image of fire and outdoors.

node.text:
You'll be asking for s'more of this beer! 🔥 
Introducing Rye Barrel Vanilla Stout, a richly textured and deliciously inky robust vanilla imperial stout. Aged in @NewRiff rye whiskey barrels for six months, flavors impart distinctive notes of earthy and peppery rye that are artfully balanced by the savory sweetness of dark malt and vanilla bean. It perfectly compliments a night by the fire, roasting up sweet treats!
This delightful treat will begin hitting shelves later this month.

node.text:
East meets West in our new stellar collaboration with @FirestoneWalker: Neon Giants. 💫 
Hops from around the world collide in this hazy supernova, with tropical fruit aromas and an exquisite nebula of flavor. Find it for a limited time starting in *August. 

*The @omgtaphouse MIGHT have it now. 😉
